{"tid":2030560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港旗 點解唔用翻黑紫荊","createTime":"2020-05-22T22:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T12:29:37.000Z","uid":321542,"like":7,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f3b071dfd5ceb1bdf7d142ca17e9fa41867f92","tid":2030560,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQB5u7w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQB5u7w.png&h=97521fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅底變黑底<br />\n代表住我地決心趕走共產黨,香港唔會染紅<br />\n<br />\n而且我地抗爭嘅時候,都有用到黑紫荊<br />\n文宣上面,掛飾貼紙都會見到<br />\n<br />\n國際層面上, 外國人睇到香港人舉旗<br />\n都會睇到黑紫荊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AY0i3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0AY0i3t.jpg&h=059fdf04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4dLu99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4dLu99.jpg&h=8418bad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨便搵cnn新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/style/article/hong-kong-flag-design-protest/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fstyle%2Farticle%2Fhong-kong-flag-design-protest%2Findex.html&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=9c223900\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fstyle%2Farticle%2Fhong-kong-flag-design-protest%2Findex.html&h=ea718b9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/style/article/hong-kong-flag-design-protest/index.html</a><br />\n黑紫荊都已經名揚國際<br />\n<br />\n最重點係<br />\n比嗰支黃黑旗好睇好多同埋更加深入人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實真正嘅最重點係, 以後睇住支黑紫荊旗<br />\n就會記得點解我地要企出嚟<br />\n亦都會記得係呢場抗爭付出嘅所有手足<br />\n<br />\n黑紫荊做香港旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. p牌仔求幫推"},{"pid":"3f791b7ce69e7fb2d82c0c2efe16da0a2b96c179","tid":2030560,"uid":62841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:39:10.000Z","msg":"屌使唔使開幾百個post呀"},{"pid":"3534ae6ede16a629a8825a7fca6cd2b0509dc9ee","tid":2030560,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:41:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82111fe5ad7afb8ecbea51bea7c6cfdb5171e22f","tid":2030560,"uid":229955,"like":1,"dislike":31,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4MCz7WJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4MCz7WJ.jpg&h=62548a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己整咗支旗<br />\n以本文前藍為底色<br />\n白色頂代表香港重光<br />\n黃色代表香港九龍新界<br />\n兩個圓圈用底色係因為想將港九新界連埋一齊<br />\n代表香港獨立"},{"pid":"7164b7e617f7ae80fbf2694eebd64e087d739a47","tid":2030560,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3f791b7ce69e7fb2d82c0c2efe16da0a2b96c179","tid":2030560,"uid":62841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:39:10.000Z","msg":"屌使唔使開幾百個post呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:45:48.000Z","msg":"最弊幾百個post都冇人提黑紫荊"},{"pid":"82b983fac601db6be4f2f7011e9cdb355307ebce","tid":2030560,"uid":199902,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:13:36.000Z","msg":"黑紫荊只係過渡，<br />\n用嚟代表，同向世人表達香港現正沉淪、侵蝕，而且當中並冇寄語希望、目標同核心價值。<br />\n做得香港旗就唔好揀黑紫荊咁負面。"},{"pid":"bce7ed92ca224d333293ef25bfbfbb7095a61dfd","tid":2030560,"uid":199902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:15:23.000Z","msg":"同埋黑紫荊對支共港共嚟講，係佢哋嘅成績表嚟。"},{"pid":"036f50306d73251b2dff5bdf2ec08a8745a710c3","tid":2030560,"uid":16878,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:23:45.000Z","msg":"點解仲要用紫荊<br />\n紫荊係用嚟笑鳩香港係混種 要人工要接種<br />\n而且洋紫荊同其他紫荊樹唔同<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係無結果嫁！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"19a6faeb841c7bcd53595756d3c1cf75effac068","tid":2030560,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"036f50306d7325